.         
.         if `a_rcsi'                     do "${c -(}dofile{c )-}/i03_rCSI.do"
{txt}
{com}. ********************************************************************************
. *                                       PART 1: rCSI Original vs. Opposite Sex
. *******************************************************************************/
.         
