> 
>         ** OUTLINE:             PART 1: Install packages and Set directories
>                                         PART 2: Organize country datasets
>                                         PART 3: Append country datasets
>                                         PART 4: Analyze Food MEB Gap  
>                                         
>         ** REQUIRES:    ${c -(}ecmen{c )-}/Bangladesh_Cox_Bazar/2_standarized_dataset/Bangladesh_Cox_Bazar_harmonized.dta
