>                                         
>         ** NOTES:               Relevant variables in each dataset: 
>                                         HHSize HHExpFood_1M HHAsstHumanCBTRec_1M
>                                         FCSCat28 rCSI Max_coping_behaviour FES
>                                         ECMEN_recomp ECMEN_SMEB_recomp
