>         ** REQUIRES:    ${c -(}ecmen{c )-}/Bangladesh_Cox_Bazar/2_standarized_dataset/Bangladesh_Cox_Bazar_harmonized.dta
>                                         ${c -(}ecmen{c )-}/Cameroon/2_standarized_dataset/Cameroon_harmonized.dta
>                                         ${c -(}ecmen{c )-}/Cameroon/2_standarized_dataset/Cameroon_harmonized.dta
>                                         ${c -(}ecmen{c )-}/Ethiopia_Tigray/2_standarized_dataset/Ethiopia_Tigray_harmonized.dta
>                                         ${c -(}ecmen{c )-}/Jordan/2_standarized_dataset/Jordan_harmonized.dta
>                                         ${c -(}ecmen{c )-}/Rwanda/2_standarized_dataset/Rwanda_harmonized.dta
